## Deployment Report: OpenWok

```
Platform:   Cloudflare Containers (primary) / Fly.io (backup)
Branch:     main
Commits:    772acf5..b9e4317 (6 deploy commits)
App status: ✅ Compiles, tests pass, serves HTTP 200 locally
```

### Done

- [x] **Dockerfile** — Dioxus 0.7 fullstack build (`dx bundle --web`), bookworm-slim runtime, proper `IP`/`PORT`/`DATABASE_PATH` env vars
- [x] **CF Containers** — `container-worker.js` using `@cloudflare/containers` SDK (singleton pattern), `wrangler.containers.jsonc` with SQLite DO binding
- [x] **Fly.io backup** — `fly.toml` (LAX region, 512MB, SQLite volume mount)
- [x] **GitHub Actions CI/CD** — `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` auto-deploys on push to main
- [x] **Build fixes** — Dioxus 0.7 import fix (`dioxus::prelude::{DioxusRouterExt, ServeConfig}`)
- [x] **Makefile** — `make deploy`, `make deploy-fly`, `make bundle` targets
- [x] `.dockerignore` — excludes target/, .git/, data/, docs/
- [x] `CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID` set as GitHub repo secret
- [x] Docker + buildx installed via colima (for future local builds)
- [x] All code pushed to `git@github.com:fortunto2/OpenWok.git`

### Manual Steps Remaining

1. **CF Containers deploy** (pick ONE):
   - **Option A — GH Actions (recommended):** Create CF API token at `dash.cloudflare.com/profile/api-tokens` (Workers + D1 permissions) → `gh secret set CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN --body "<token>"` → push triggers auto-deploy
   - **Option B — Local:** `colima start && make deploy` (builds Docker under QEMU, ~30 min on ARM Mac)
   - **Option C — Fly.io:** `fly auth login && fly deploy --remote-only` (remote x86 build, fastest)

2. **Custom domain** — already configured at `openwok.superduperai.co` (Worker routes active)

3. **Environment variables** (post-deploy):
   - `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY` — for payment processing
   - `SUPABASE_URL` / `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` — for auth
   - `POSTHOG_API_KEY` — for analytics

